  <description>
    <p>Mini EQ provides a compact GTK interface for a system-wide parametric equalizer on PipeWire desktops.</p>
    <p>It creates a PipeWire filter-chain sink using builtin biquad filters and can route output streams through the processed sink.</p>
  </description>
